{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/aws/aws_1_10/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Devlog","author":"JonginPark","siteUrl":"https://SiverPineValley.github.io","comment":{"disqusShortName":"","utterances":"SiverPineValley/devlog"},"sponsor":{"buyMeACoffeeId":""}}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"8117b01d-5131-5ab7-a0be-7c2b4597bd9e","excerpt":"한 번의 로그인 (Single Sign-On)으로 다음 서비스들에 자동으로 로그인 연동을 제공 AWS accounts in AWS Organizations Business cloud applications (Salesforce, Box, Microsoft 365) SAML2.0-enabled applications EC2 Windows Instances 개인정보 제공자들 IAM Identity Center내의 빌트인 개인정보 저장소 서드 파티: Active Directory (AD…","html":"<ul>\n<li>한 번의 로그인 (Single Sign-On)으로 다음 서비스들에 자동으로 로그인 연동을 제공\n<ul>\n<li>AWS accounts in AWS Organizations</li>\n<li>Business cloud applications (Salesforce, Box, Microsoft 365)</li>\n<li>SAML2.0-enabled applications</li>\n<li>EC2 Windows Instances</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>개인정보 제공자들\n<ul>\n<li>IAM Identity Center내의 빌트인 개인정보 저장소</li>\n<li>서드 파티: Active Directory (AD), OneLogin, Okta…</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</br>\n<div align=\"left\">\n  <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1200px; \">\n      <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 46%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" alt=\"aws iam identity center\" title=\"\" src=\"/static/0a83bae0b8ef731f74518431881800ed/c1b63/aws_iam_identity_center.png\" srcset=\"/static/0a83bae0b8ef731f74518431881800ed/5a46d/aws_iam_identity_center.png 300w,\n/static/0a83bae0b8ef731f74518431881800ed/0a47e/aws_iam_identity_center.png 600w,\n/static/0a83bae0b8ef731f74518431881800ed/c1b63/aws_iam_identity_center.png 1200w,\n/static/0a83bae0b8ef731f74518431881800ed/1dbe8/aws_iam_identity_center.png 1374w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n    </span>\n</div>\n<br>\n<div align=\"left\">\n  <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1200px; \">\n      <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 46%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" alt=\"aws iam identity center 2\" title=\"\" src=\"/static/9740a03b3c28ff50db4192aa7abd94fa/c1b63/aws_iam_identity_center_2.png\" srcset=\"/static/9740a03b3c28ff50db4192aa7abd94fa/5a46d/aws_iam_identity_center_2.png 300w,\n/static/9740a03b3c28ff50db4192aa7abd94fa/0a47e/aws_iam_identity_center_2.png 600w,\n/static/9740a03b3c28ff50db4192aa7abd94fa/c1b63/aws_iam_identity_center_2.png 1200w,\n/static/9740a03b3c28ff50db4192aa7abd94fa/5a791/aws_iam_identity_center_2.png 1248w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n    </span>\n</div>\n<br>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>다중 계정 권한</strong>\n<ul>\n<li>AWS 조직 내의 AWS 계정들 간에 액세스를 관리합니다.</li>\n<li>권한 설정 - AWS 접근을 정의하기 위해 하나 혹은 여러 개의 IAM 정책들의 모음을 유저, 그룹에 할당</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><strong>Application 권한 설정</strong>\n<ul>\n<li>많은 SAML 2.0 비즈니스 애플리케이션들 (Salesforce, Box, Microsoft 365) 로의 SSO 접근</li>\n<li>필요한 URL, 인증, 메타데이터 제공</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><strong>속성 기반 접근 제어 (ABAC, Attribute-Based Access Control)</strong>\n<ul>\n<li>IAM Identity Center Identity Store에 저장된 유저의 속성에 기반한 세밀한 권한 제어</li>\n<li>권한을 정의하고, 속성을 변경하여 AWS 접근을 수정할 때 설정</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</br>\n<div align=\"left\">\n  <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 426px; \">\n      <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 125.66666666666669%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" alt=\"aws iam identity center 3\" title=\"\" src=\"/static/8510b308a9a52bd5df2a5919fbc89b70/531e1/aws_iam_identity_center_3.png\" srcset=\"/static/8510b308a9a52bd5df2a5919fbc89b70/5a46d/aws_iam_identity_center_3.png 300w,\n/static/8510b308a9a52bd5df2a5919fbc89b70/531e1/aws_iam_identity_center_3.png 426w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 426px) 100vw, 426px\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n    </span>\n</div>\n<br>","frontmatter":{"title":"1-10) AWS IAM Identity Center (AWS Single Sign-On)","date":"June 15, 2025"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/aws/aws_1_10/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/aws/aws_1_9/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"1-9) IAM Permission Boundaries"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/aws/aws_1_11/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"1-11) AWS Active Directory (AD)"}}}},"staticQueryHashes":["3128451518","643154061"],"slicesMap":{}}